📍Norway 🇵🇸♥️🇳🇴 
GOOD MORNING, NRK.
Early on Thursday morning, 29 February, a convoy of aid drove into Gaza City. Large crowds of malnourished and starving Palestinians ran towards the trucks to get food and flour. Israeli soldiers opened fire and shot at the crowd. At least 110 people have been confirmed killed and 700 injured.
Every morning until the Eurovision final, the Action Group for Palestine demonstrates outside the national broadcaster.
We ask NRK to follow its moral responsibility, as they did after Russia’s attack on Ukraine two years ago: NRK must demand the exclusion of Israel from Eurovision 2024.

